{"tid":609410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得啲茶餐廳拎著「小店光環」賣野賣到好貴，好嘔心?","createTime":"2018-03-29T04:33:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T07:28:55.000Z","uid":42188,"like":41,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c088781d4663dd3030a96440792020e4e60c9d24","tid":609410,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T04:33:59.000Z","msg":"以焗豬扒飯為例<br />\n大家樂，大快活都係$45左右<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解同區既茶餐廳要賣到$60<br />\n我唔覺得因為茶餐廳係小店，成本比連鎖店高到要貴成$10幾,$20先圍到本<br />\n<br />\n仲有，係茶餐廳食慢啲都俾啲姐姐啤著，未食完就收咗你碟飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁點解我唔去返連鎖店食?"},{"pid":"923b978bcbfc160324e0f385b336a0c1daca0bc9","tid":609410,"uid":82312,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T05:21:55.000Z","msg":"M記26蚊個餐加一蚊都比人屌垃圾食物<br />\n茶記三十幾走唔甩 啲薯條仲垃圾 個個話下午茶底食"},{"pid":"637595e2c4ce8ae46ac1601df92a20e4d21a0804","tid":609410,"uid":48531,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T05:33:56.000Z","msg":"餐紙都冇 唔乾淨連打掃都懶 服務差 價錢貴 根本不思進取 又話財團迫害小店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fecb483cdbcfd993ac7025a4c535ad94b7ddcf8e","tid":609410,"uid":35814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T05:40:25.000Z","msg":"我覺得主要係租金問題<br />\n唔講食物質素<br />\n喺彩虹都食過午餐$40有找<br />\n有飯有野飲嘅茶記<br />\n晚餐都係多$2至$5有埋湯<br />\n<br />\n但行過少少去采頤、坪石就至少$50一餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c29ce78499c010ae24676623520b409641e8ee5f","tid":609410,"uid":142314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T05:43:40.000Z","msg":"連鎖係量產<br />\n<br />\n茶記你唔係叫午、快、常餐，肯定貴啲"},{"pid":"a38b452d9c62e85bf21d9e3cd0b3dacf2f37ffab","tid":609410,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c29ce78499c010ae24676623520b409641e8ee5f","tid":609410,"uid":142314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T05:43:40.000Z","msg":"連鎖係量產<br />\n<br />\n茶記你唔係叫午、快、常餐，肯定貴啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTim